>>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
*> 30VOCAC0 — documents: the controlled vocabulary control, mirroring
*> ControlledVocabulary.java. Ops:
*>   NORM validate/normalize a raw class value (200 + canonical
*>        upper-case code, or 404 when outside the vocabulary)
*>   LIST all classes sorted by name  CREA create  UPDT update  DELE
*> V-STATUS is HTTP-shaped (200/201/404/409/422), V-MSG verbatim as-is.
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. "30VOCAC0".
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-OP                PIC X(4).
01 WS-RET               PIC X(2).
COPY "30CLASR0.cpy" REPLACING ==:PFX:== BY ==WS-CL==.
01 WS-CL-TABLE.
   05 WS-CL-COUNT       PIC 9(4).
   05 WS-CL-ROW OCCURS 100.
      10 WS-CL-ROW-ID   PIC X(36).
      10 WS-CL-ROW-NAME PIC X(50).
      10 WS-CL-ROW-DESC PIC X(200).
01 WS-CODE              PIC X(50).
01 WS-UUID              PIC X(36).
01 WS-EPOCH             PIC 9(13).
LINKAGE SECTION.
01 V-OP                 PIC X(4).
01 V-STATUS             PIC X(3).
01 V-MSG                PIC X(200).
01 V-NAME               PIC X(200).
01 V-DESC               PIC X(200).
COPY "30CLASR0.cpy" REPLACING ==:PFX:== BY ==V-CL==.
01 V-CL-TABLE.
   05 V-CL-COUNT        PIC 9(4).
   05 V-CL-ROW OCCURS 100.
      10 V-CL-ROW-ID    PIC X(36).
      10 V-CL-ROW-NAME  PIC X(50).
      10 V-CL-ROW-DESC  PIC X(200).
PROCEDURE DIVISION USING V-OP V-STATUS V-MSG V-NAME V-DESC
                         V-CL-REC V-CL-TABLE.
MAIN.
    MOVE SPACES TO V-MSG
    EVALUATE V-OP
        WHEN "NORM" PERFORM DO-NORMALIZE
        WHEN "LIST" PERFORM DO-LIST
        WHEN "CREA" PERFORM DO-CREATE
        WHEN "UPDT" PERFORM DO-UPDATE
        WHEN "DELE" PERFORM DO-DELETE
        WHEN OTHER
            MOVE "422" TO V-STATUS
            MOVE "unknown operation" TO V-MSG
    END-EVALUATE
    GOBACK.

DO-NORMALIZE.
    IF FUNCTION TRIM (V-NAME) = SPACES
        MOVE "404" TO V-STATUS
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
    END-IF
    MOVE FUNCTION UPPER-CASE (FUNCTION TRIM (V-NAME)) TO WS-CODE
    MOVE SPACES TO V-CL-REC
    MOVE WS-CODE TO V-CL-NAME
    MOVE "NAME" TO WS-OP
    CALL "30CLASE0" USING WS-OP WS-RET V-CL-REC V-CL-TABLE
    IF WS-RET = "00"
        MOVE "200" TO V-STATUS
    ELSE
        MOVE "404" TO V-STATUS
    END-IF.

DO-LIST.
    MOVE SPACES TO V-CL-REC
    MOVE "ALL " TO WS-OP
    CALL "30CLASE0" USING WS-OP WS-RET V-CL-REC V-CL-TABLE
    MOVE "200" TO V-STATUS.

DO-CREATE.
    PERFORM REQUIRE-NAME
    IF V-STATUS = "422"
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
    END-IF
    PERFORM REQUIRE-DESCRIPTION
    IF V-STATUS = "422"
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
    END-IF
    MOVE SPACES TO WS-CL-REC
    MOVE WS-CODE TO WS-CL-NAME
    MOVE "NAME" TO WS-OP
    CALL "30CLASE0" USING WS-OP WS-RET WS-CL-REC WS-CL-TABLE
    IF WS-RET = "00"
        PERFORM CONFLICT-EXISTS
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
    END-IF
    CALL "00UUIDC0" USING WS-UUID WS-EPOCH
    MOVE SPACES TO V-CL-REC
    MOVE WS-UUID TO V-CL-ID
    MOVE WS-CODE TO V-CL-NAME
    MOVE FUNCTION TRIM (V-DESC) TO V-CL-DESC
    MOVE WS-EPOCH TO V-CL-CREATED
    MOVE "WRT " TO WS-OP
    CALL "30CLASE0" USING WS-OP WS-RET V-CL-REC V-CL-TABLE
    IF WS-RET = "22"
        PERFORM CONFLICT-EXISTS
    ELSE
        MOVE "201" TO V-STATUS
    END-IF.

DO-UPDATE.
    MOVE "GET " TO WS-OP
    CALL "30CLASE0" USING WS-OP WS-RET V-CL-REC V-CL-TABLE
    IF WS-RET NOT = "00"
        MOVE "404" TO V-STATUS
        MOVE "not found" TO V-MSG
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
    END-IF
    PERFORM REQUIRE-NAME
    IF V-STATUS = "422"
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
    END-IF
    PERFORM REQUIRE-DESCRIPTION
    IF V-STATUS = "422"
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
    END-IF
    IF WS-CODE NOT = V-CL-NAME
        MOVE SPACES TO WS-CL-REC
        MOVE WS-CODE TO WS-CL-NAME
        MOVE "NAME" TO WS-OP
        CALL "30CLASE0" USING WS-OP WS-RET WS-CL-REC WS-CL-TABLE
        IF WS-RET = "00"
            PERFORM CONFLICT-EXISTS
            EXIT PARAGRAPH
        END-IF
    END-IF
    MOVE WS-CODE TO V-CL-NAME
    MOVE FUNCTION TRIM (V-DESC) TO V-CL-DESC
    MOVE "REW " TO WS-OP
    CALL "30CLASE0" USING WS-OP WS-RET V-CL-REC V-CL-TABLE
    MOVE "200" TO V-STATUS.

DO-DELETE.
    MOVE "GET " TO WS-OP
    CALL "30CLASE0" USING WS-OP WS-RET V-CL-REC V-CL-TABLE
    IF WS-RET NOT = "00"
        MOVE "404" TO V-STATUS
        MOVE "not found" TO V-MSG
        EXIT PARAGRAPH
    END-IF
    MOVE "DEL " TO WS-OP
    CALL "30CLASE0" USING WS-OP WS-RET V-CL-REC V-CL-TABLE
    MOVE "200" TO V-STATUS.

REQUIRE-NAME.
    IF FUNCTION TRIM (V-NAME) = SPACES
        MOVE "422" TO V-STATUS
        MOVE "document class name is required" TO V-MSG
    ELSE
        MOVE FUNCTION UPPER-CASE (FUNCTION TRIM (V-NAME)) TO WS-CODE
    END-IF.

REQUIRE-DESCRIPTION.
    IF FUNCTION TRIM (V-DESC) = SPACES
        MOVE "422" TO V-STATUS
        MOVE "document class description is required" TO V-MSG
    END-IF.

CONFLICT-EXISTS.
    MOVE "409" TO V-STATUS
    MOVE SPACES TO V-MSG
    STRING "document class already exists: "
           FUNCTION TRIM (WS-CODE)
        DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO V-MSG
    END-STRING.
END PROGRAM "30VOCAC0".
